description: This file declares APIs for managing TelcoVoice settings, including functions to get, set, validate, commit, and rollback configurations related to X_RDK_TelcoVoice.

methods.name: X_RDK_TelcoVoice_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves the value of a specified string parameter related to TelcoVoice.

methods.name: X_RDK_TelcoVoice_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets the value of a specified string parameter related to TelcoVoice.

methods.name: X_RDK_TelcoVoice_Validate
methods.description: Validates the current configuration parameters for TelcoVoice.

methods.name: X_RDK_TelcoVoice_Commit
methods.description: Commits the current TelcoVoice configuration changes.

methods.name: X_RDK_TelcoVoice_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back any uncommitted changes to TelcoVoice configuration.
